<div class="com-share" data-id="24029" data-title="《电视剧拿下金球奖，亚马逊的电影也要冲击奥斯卡》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/24029/medium/24029.jpg?1458189290" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/24029.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
